                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/9432: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-08-17T15:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 17, 1937—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>150. Your 272, August 16, 6 p.m. I heartily approve your action and excellent
                    note. If not already done, please inform your British and, in your discretion,
                    French colleague.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
